title: Young Hannah, Queen of the Vampires (1973) CRYPT OF THE LIVING DEAD

sources.title: Young Hannah, Queen of the Vampires (1973) CRYPT OF THE LIVING DEAD
sources.description:
It's Friday@PizzaFLIX
Stars: Teresa Gimera, Andrew Prine, Mark Damon, Patty Shepard
Director: Julio Salvador
The exotic Catalonia beauty Teresa Gimera stars as the former bride of Louis VII entombed for centuries in a Crypt of the Living Dead. Accidentally released after 700 years, the insatiable bloodsucker goes on a ravenous rampage!
